      <title>TotalEnergies 不再通过红海派遣船只</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/totalenergies-no-longer-sending-ships-through-red-sea-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国石油巨头TotalEnergies周三表示，该公司已经好几个星期没有派遣船只通过通往红海和苏伊士运河的南部海峡，延长了其船只前往欧洲的航行时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/totalenergies-no-longer-sending-ships-through-red-sea-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:14:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞安航空再次赢得针对荷兰皇家航空救助的法庭诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/eu-court-again-backs-ryanair-challenge-against-dutch-bailout-klm-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，瑞安航空赢得了针对法航荷航荷兰子公司 34 亿欧元（合 37 亿美元）的荷兰救助计划的第二次挑战，此前欧洲第二最高法院表示，欧盟竞争监管机构没有考虑该航空集团内的其他受益人，这是错误的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/eu-court-again-backs-ryanair-challenge-against-dutch-bailout-klm-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:52:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国新能源汽车销量自8月以来首次环比下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-new-energy-vehicle-sales-fall-388-jan-mm-first-such-drop-since-aug-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业数据显示，中国新能源汽车销量环比下降38.8%，这是自2023年8月以来的首次下降，尽管特斯拉领衔的新一轮打折活动，但全球最大汽车市场的需求仍出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-new-energy-vehicle-sales-fall-388-jan-mm-first-such-drop-since-aug-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:48:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挑战依然存在，风电巨头对 2024 年前景黯淡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/wind-power-giants-give-bleak-view-2024-challenges-persist-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球三大风电集团周三对未来一年发表了冷静的看法，指出成熟行业面临持续的挑战，该行业继续遭受项目延误、设备问题和通货膨胀的困扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/wind-power-giants-give-bleak-view-2024-challenges-persist-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚允许工人在下班后忽略老板的电话</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-allow-workers-ignore-after-hours-calls-bosses-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚将出台法律，赋予工人在工作时间之外无视老板无理电话和信息的权利，而不会受到处罚，违反规定的雇主可能会被处以罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-allow-workers-ignore-after-hours-calls-bosses-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查：新兴市场货币短期内将稳步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-currencies-gain-steadily-near-term-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透对外汇策略师的一项调查发现，随着美联储大幅降息的预期减弱，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元汇率在未来几个月将难以收复今年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-currencies-gain-steadily-near-term-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
